					</div>
					<a href="/Letter_of_Recommendation_prof_Hamhalter.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="action-btn" style="padding: 0.6rem 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--accent); color: #000;">Read Full Letter</a>
